summary: Look at me. Okay, what do you want ?
descriptionHtml:
[url=http://skse.silverlock.org/]This mod requires Skyrim Script Extender 1.6.7 or higher[/url] ! No other versions are supported !

This simple mod allows you to open the vendor dialogue by looking at the vendor. That\'s it ! It will save you the pain of going through the dialogue ; because you are lazy.

Oh yes, yes you are.

[youtube]7eDpl97Upj0[/youtube]
author: Sagittarius22
